@startuml
actor Maintainer
participant "Inventario" as Inv
participant "Research" as Research
participant "Data Model" as DM

Maintainer -> Inv: listar 13 modulos legados
Inv -> Research: registrar decisao (migrar/adaptar/adiar/descartar)
Research --> Inv: rationale e riscos
Inv -> DM: atualizar estados e campos
DM --> Inv: rastreabilidade consolidada
Inv --> Maintainer: inventario completo e validavel
@enduml
